
'''= belgian festival for 'equality', last held in Ghent, Belgium in December 2016'''

URL : http://www.festivalgelijkheid.be/



=Description=

Festival van de Gelijkheid (Translation: Festival for Equality) is an event hosted in Ghent, Belgium in December. The event has been running since 2012 and aims to celebrate celebrate and highlight equality through a diverse range of debates, literature, exhibitions, interviews, music, performance, theater, documentaries, urban art, book exchanges, poetry slams and more. 


